Description: Provides native R bindings to the 'minibwa' short-read aligner
    with raw-vector query input, external-pointer alignment batches, ALTREP
    column views, and an installed C API for downstream packages. The package
    builds staged Single Instruction Multiple Data ('SIMD') KSW backends and
    selects portable scalar, SSE4, or AVX2 code at runtime without global
    instruction-set compiler flags.
License: GPL (>= 2)
